This file acts as a template for users to follow. It identifies all required variables without exposing your actual credentials.

Bash

# --- OpenClaw Environment Variables Template ---
# Copy this file to '.env' and fill in your actual credentials.
# DO NOT commit your actual '.env' file to GitHub.

# 1. API Configurations (OpenRouter / OpenAI)

OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-your-key-here
MODEL=openrouter/qwen/qwen3-vl-30b-a3b-thinking:free

# 2. Telegram Bot Integration

# Obtain from @BotFather on Telegram
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=your_bot_token_here

# 3. OpenClaw Gateway Security

# Token generated during deployment for system pairing
OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_TOKEN=your_gateway_token_here
